entry.string: There are currently no category links in the database...
entry.translation: Zeere-a ere-a coorrently nu cetegury leenks in zee detebese-a...

entry.string: By clicking on Delete you can delete all category links associated with a particular module. Clicking on a module will take you to that module's statistics page containing the figures for each of that module's items that have category links associated with them. From there you can delete all category links associated with a particular item.
entry.translation: By cleecking oon Delete-a yuoo cun delete-a ell cetegury leenks essuceeeted veet a perteecooler mudoole-a. Cleecking oon a mudoole-a veell teke-a yuoo tu thet mudoole's steteestics pege-a cunteeening zee feegoores fur iech ooff thet mudoole's items thet hefe-a cetegury leenks essuceeeted veet zeem. Frum zeere-a yuoo cun delete-a ell cetegury leenks essuceeeted veet a perteecooler item.

entry.string: There are currently no category links attached to this module...
entry.translation: Zeere-a ere-a coorrently nu cetegury leenks etteched tu thees mudoole-a...

entry.string: By clicking on Delete you can delete all category links associated with a particular module's item.
entry.translation: By cleecking oon Delete-a yuoo cun delete-a ell cetegury leenks essuceeeted veet a perteecooler mudoole's item.
